# Age Calculator

An easy-to-use **Age Calculator** web application that calculates a userâ€™s exact age in **Years, Months, and Days** based on their Date of Birth.

This project is built using simple **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript** and is perfect for beginners to understand date handling and basic web development.

